#: ../../source/api/HistoryPanel.rst:2
msgid "HistoryPanel 类"
msgstr "HistoryPanel Class"

#: ../../source/api/HistoryPanel.rst:4
msgid "历史数据类 HistoryPanel 及相关辅助函数。"
msgstr "History Data Class HistoryPanel:"

#: ../../source/api/HistoryPanel.rst:7
msgid "HistoryPanel 数据结构与切片"
msgstr "HistoryPanel Data Structure and Slicing"

#: ../../source/api/HistoryPanel.rst:9
msgid "HistoryPanel 本质上是一个三维 ``numpy.ndarray``，三个轴分别表示："
msgstr ""
"HistoryPanel is essentially a three-dimensional ``numpy.ndarray``, with the "
"three axes representing:"

#: ../../source/api/HistoryPanel.rst:11
msgid "axis 0 / levels: 标的维度，每一层对应一只股票或一个指数，标签列表为 ``shares``；"
msgstr ""
"axis 0 / levels: instrument dimension; each level corresponds to a stock or "
"an index, and the label list is ``shares``;"

#: ../../source/api/HistoryPanel.rst:12
msgid "axis 1 / rows: 时间维度，每一行对应一个时间点，标签列表为 ``hdates``；"
msgstr ""
"axis 1 / rows: time dimension; each row corresponds to a point in time, and "
"the label list is ``hdates``;"

#: ../../source/api/HistoryPanel.rst:13
msgid "axis 2 / columns: 历史数据类型维度，每一列对应一种数据类型，标签列表为 ``htypes``。"
msgstr ""
"axis 2 / columns: historical data type dimension; each column corresponds to"
" a data type, and the label list is ``htypes``."

#: ../../source/api/HistoryPanel.rst:15
msgid ""
"借助这三个轴标签，可以通过方括号 ``[]`` 对 HistoryPanel 进行灵活切片，基本规则为 ``[htype_slicer, "
"share_slicer, date_slicer]``；省略维度时与单段写法 （如 ``hp['close']``）仍返回子 "
"``HistoryPanel`` （带轴标签），裸矩阵请用 ``.values`` / ``.to_numpy()``。"
msgstr ""
"With these three axis labels, you can flexibly slice a HistoryPanel using "
"square brackets ``[]``. The basic rule is ``[htype_slicer, share_slicer, "
"date_slicer]``; when dimensions are omitted, the single-segment form (e.g., "
"``hp['close']``) still returns a sub-``HistoryPanel`` (with axis labels). "
"For a raw matrix, use ``.values`` / ``.to_numpy()``."

#: ../../source/api/HistoryPanel.rst:18
msgid ""
"时间轴 （第三段）还支持：单个 ``pandas.Timestamp``、时间标签列表、长度 ``L = len(hdates)`` 的一维 "
"``bool`` 列表或 ``numpy`` 一维 ``bool`` 数组；与只读属性 ``hp.loc[key]`` 等价于 ``hp[:, :, "
"key]``。格点级 ``(M, L, N)`` 布尔掩码不属于 ``loc`` / 第三轴索引语义，请用 "
":meth:`~qteasy.HistoryPanel.where`。"
msgstr ""
"The time axis (the third axis) also supports: a single ``pandas.Timestamp``,"
" a list of time labels, a 1D ``bool`` list of length ``L = len(hdates)``, or"
" a 1D ``numpy`` ``bool`` array; the read-only property ``hp.loc[key]`` is "
"equivalent to ``hp[:, :, key]``. A grid-level ``(M, L, N)`` boolean mask is "
"not part of the ``loc`` / third-axis indexing semantics; use "
":meth:`~qteasy.HistoryPanel.where` instead."

#: ../../source/api/HistoryPanel.rst:20
msgid "典型写法示例::"
msgstr "Typical writing example::"

#: of qteasy.history.HistoryPanel:1
msgid "qteasy 中用于统一管理多标的、多时间点、多数据类型历史数据的三维数据容器。"
msgstr ""
"In qteasy, it is a three-dimensional data container used to centrally manage"
" historical data across multiple instruments, multiple time points, and "
"multiple data types."

#: of qteasy.history.HistoryPanel:3
msgid "HistoryPanel 本质是一个三维 ``numpy.ndarray``，三条轴分别表示标的 （shares）、时间"
msgstr ""
"HistoryPanel is essentially a three-dimensional ``numpy.ndarray``, and the "
"three axes represent the instrument (shares) and time"

#: of qteasy.history.HistoryPanel:4
msgid "（hdates）和历史数据类型 （htypes），支持按任意轴灵活切片、重标记以及与"
msgstr ""
"(hdates) and historical data types (htypes), supporting flexible slicing and"
" relabeling along any axis, as well as mutual conversion with"

#: of qteasy.history.HistoryPanel:5
msgid "pandas DataFrame 之间的互相转换，并作为 get_history_data 与可视化栈"
msgstr ""
"pandas DataFrame, and serving as the data container for get_history_data and"
" the visualization stack"

#: of qteasy.history.HistoryPanel:6
msgid "（如 ``HistoryPanel.plot()`` 与 ``qt.candle``）之间的核心桥梁。"
msgstr ""
"the core bridge (e.g., between ``HistoryPanel.plot()`` and ``qt.candle``)."

#: of qteasy.history.HistoryPanel:8
msgid ""
"**索引与数组出口**：``__getitem__`` 始终返回带正确轴标签的子 ``HistoryPanel``；需要 裸 ``ndarray`` "
"时用 ``.values`` 或 ``.to_numpy(copy=...)``。**单列原地赋值** ``panel['列名'] = value`` "
"由 ``__setitem__`` 实现 （仅非空面板、仅 ``str`` 键）， 值广播为 ``(标的数, 时间长度)`` 并以 "
"``float64`` 存储；覆盖已有列或追加新列。 子面板与父对象共享缓冲时的语义见 ``__getitem__`` / ``subpanel`` /"
" ``__setitem__`` 各方法说明。"
msgstr ""
"**Indexing and array export**: ``__getitem__`` always returns a "
"sub-``HistoryPanel`` with correct axis labels; when you need a raw "
"``ndarray``, use ``.values`` or ``.to_numpy(copy=...)``. **In-place "
"assignment to a single column** ``panel['column_name'] = value`` is "
"implemented by ``__setitem__`` (only for non-empty panels, and only for "
"``str`` keys). The value is broadcast to ``(number_of_shares, time_length)``"
" and stored as ``float64``; it overwrites an existing column or appends a "
"new one. For semantics when a sub-panel shares the buffer with its parent, "
"see the docs for ``__getitem__`` / ``subpanel`` / ``__setitem__``."

#: of qteasy.history.HistoryPanel:14
msgid ""
"**体验向 API**：合法 Python 标识符且存在于 ``htypes`` 的列名可用属性只读访问 （如 ``panel.close``， 等价 "
"``panel['close']``）；比较运算 （如 ``panel.close > panel.open``）返回 ``numpy`` 布尔数组； "
"``panel.loc[key]`` 等价 ``panel[:, :, key]``，仅沿时间轴筛选 （不接 ``where`` 的三维掩码）。 "
"用户文档见 Sphinx **HistoryPanel** 页与教程「使用 HistoryPanel 操作和分析历史数据」 （§6 及 §6.1）。"
msgstr ""
"**Ergonomics-oriented API**: column names that are valid Python identifiers "
"and exist in ``htypes`` can be accessed read-only as attributes (e.g. "
"``panel.close``, equivalent to ``panel['close']``); comparison operations "
"(e.g. ``panel.close > panel.open``) return a ``numpy`` boolean array; "
"``panel.loc[key]`` is equivalent to ``panel[:, :, key]``, filtering only "
"along the time axis (it does not accept a 3D mask like ``where``). User "
"docs: the Sphinx **HistoryPanel** page and the tutorial “Using HistoryPanel "
"to manipulate and analyze historical data” (§6 and §6.1)."

#: of qteasy.history.HistoryPanel:19
msgid "更详细的结构说明 （轴标签、切片示例、标签管理等）见文档「HistoryPanel 类」相关章节。"
msgstr ""
"For a more detailed structural description (axis labels, slicing examples, "
"label management, etc.), see the relevant section in the documentation "
"“HistoryPanel class”."

#: of qteasy.history.HistoryPanel.__eq__:1
msgid "逐元素 ``self == other``；不支持的类型返回 ``NotImplemented``。"
msgstr ""
"Element-wise ``self == other``; unsupported types return ``NotImplemented``."

